{"tid":1379292,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"腳中槍嗰位戰友 希望你可以無事快啲好返","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:45:48.000Z","uid":59305,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50d551363e85b272e03b66d5dea4e17406e9159c","tid":1379292,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%81%E6%9C%A8%E7%9B%BE-%E7%9C%9F%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E6%80%95-%E8%AB%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%98%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25AF%2581%25E6%259C%25A8%25E7%259B%25BE-%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2580%2595-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E5%2598%2585%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e638ba37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F728-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25AF%2581%25E6%259C%25A8%25E7%259B%25BE-%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2580%2595-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%25E5%2598%2585%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%2F&h=371e4690\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/728-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%81%E6%9C%A8%E7%9B%BE-%E7%9C%9F%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E6%80%95-%E8%AB%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E5%98%85%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82/</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚發咗個同報導好相似嘅夢<br />\n少少感想<br />\n<br />\n首先多謝大盾戰友 如果無你 我諗中槍先嗰個係我 事關有粒彈直接命中咗個盾 極大&quot;砰&quot;一聲打中 真係嚇撚親 但個盾無爆到 好堅! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係腳中槍位戰友 其實就喺我右手邊 當粒彈打中大盾後 我地緩緩退後 突然間你就跌落地下 即時去扶起你但你無任何反應 以為你暈咗 望一望你隻腳已經流緊血 先知你中槍 所以成班手足就合力抬你去後方 希望你無事 快d好返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我地枱腳中槍位爸打去後方旁邊 打算等急救時 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班狗一定見到有傷者瞓咗喺旁邊 但佢地仍然不斷開槍同放催淚煙 兼且同時推進 完全唔理人命</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n當時喺槍聲此起彼落 以及帶咗豬嘴嘅情況之下 跟本無first aid聽到 所以情急之下 我叫其他人抬戰友向後走 我跑後少少除咗豬嘴後大嗌first aid 就係呢一刻不慎吸入大量催淚煙 即時咳到仆街 完全抖唔到氣 跟住跪低咗 差唔多暈咁濟 好彩有位戰友即時扶起我 托住我行 而另一位戰友就幫手開路 真係好多謝 好感激你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想多謝立場新聞 有你地 香港人先睇到更多真相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再最後少少感想就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺最前排 班狗係咁開槍 話唔驚就呃你嘅<br />\n但更感受到嘅係安心 因為身邊係有班齊上齊落 唔會離棄你嘅香港人<br />\n非常榮幸能夠同你哋並肩作戰 Love you all<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ec9f8c99769a37d4f9da638f4f64bf6370f49f1","tid":1379292,"uid":24713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝願所有受傷被捕手足都快d 冇事<br />\n<br />\n一齊屌爆班狗<img src=\"/ass